-  <p>The situation at large is clear. The era of AI acting as a harmless chatbot is over. Agents are moving into the enterprise, and they are being handed the keys to real operations. But you cannot safely scale autonomous AI if you cannot trust the final point of execution.</p>
-
-  <p>The rest of this whitepaper breaks down the exact mechanics of the HoloEngine architecture. It details the hard data from our ablation tests, the unexpected failures we exposed in our own system, and the strict structural rules required to close the gap. We are not just pointing out a theoretical risk. We are providing the <strong>engineering blueprint for trusted delegation.</strong></p>
